name: Extra's Death: I Am the Son of Hades
summary:
A no-name character that never appeared in the novel.

An extra.

Neo became that extra character.

...

Transmigrating into the novel and gaining the bloodline of Hades, the God of Death, was supposed to be the best thing to happen in Neos life.

So

Why?

[Unique Skill: Death]

[Skill Effect: You die]

Why did he awaken this damned skill!?
author: FailedWriter101
